Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Democrats take Senate
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xsbm
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Nov 1986
Reagan may get a bumpy ride in his last two years as Senate goes to the Democrats in off-year elections. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less